Macros
SDIO status register bits
UDB_SDIO » Macros

General Description

Macros

#define SDIO_STS_CMD_DONE   (0x01u)
 The command is done.
 
#define SDIO_STS_WRITE_DONE   (0x02u)
 All data for a write has been sent.
 
#define SDIO_STS_READ_DONE   (0x04u)
 All data for a read has been read.
 
#define SDIO_STS_CRC_ERR   (0x08u)
 A CRC error was detected during a read or write.
 
#define SDIO_STS_CMD_IDLE   (0x10u)
 The command channel is idle.
 
#define SDIO_STS_DAT_IDLE   (0x20u)
 The data channel is idle.
 
#define SDIO_STS_CARD_INT   (0x40u)
 The SDIO card indicated an interrupt by driving DAT[1] low.
